44 This bill is a concept draft pursuant to Joint Rule 208.
5 This bill proposes to convene a stakeholder group to study the long-term solvency of
6 the Maine Guaranteed Access Reinsurance Association and to make recommendations to
7 the Legislature regarding solutions to ensure that the association remains solvent.
